        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Architecture is not decoration. It\u2019s the physical framework of daily life \u2014 the light in a kitchen, the threshold between public and private, the way a building meets the ground. We design with that responsibility in mind.</p>",
